The New Mayo Clinic Diet is the only weight loss program that features a comprehensive, whole-health menu program developed and approved by Mayo Clinic. Our flexible meal plans fit into any lifestyle, and our easy to prepare recipes show you how good food can be great — and great for you, too.



This app is your companion to the New Mayo Clinic Diet digital platform, and it includes all the essentials you need on the go, such as:

>> Meal Plan featuring the Original Mayo Clinic Diet, Healthy Keto, Higher Protein, Vegetarian or Mediterranean menus, which ever one you choose.

>> Habit Optimizer to swap unhealthy habits for healthy ones.

>> Food Tracker with over 1 million foods to help you keep track of your Mayo Clinic food group servings.

>> Weight Tracker to record your weight, body measurements and weigh-in selfies

>> More features coming soon!
